      {
        "nameNarration": "十七夜",
        "narration": "―十七夜―@虽然当调整师的保镖也挺有趣的@但再怎么说，我也没办法离开这里",
        "narrationAnchor": "bottom",
        "narrationCoverOpacity": 110,
        "narrationEffect": "in",
        "narrationFontSize": 30,
        "narrationLineMargin": 10,
        "narrationLineSpace": 20,
        "turnChangeOut": "fadeOut",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-16"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―十七夜―@大家已经连结起了东西的关系",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-17"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―十七夜―@为了让学生会议进一步发展@我和八云打算继续留在神滨市",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-18"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "御魂",
        "narration": "―御魂―@而且，这座城市里还有很多@我深爱的魔法少女",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-19"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―御魂―@我不想再被自己的感情支配，并背叛她们了",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-20"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "莉薇娅",
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@嘛，毕竟御魂那里有桃子在@东边也有很多仰慕十七夜的人吧",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-21"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@和被世界抛弃的我们可不一样",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-22"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "御魂",
        "narration": "―御魂―@那么，老师在这之后也只是打算@作为调整师巡游各地吗…？",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-23"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "莉薇娅",
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@我们会一如既往地，帮想打倒的家伙干活",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-24"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@总之，把这家伙也带上",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-25"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "丘比",
        "narration": "―丘比―@莉薇娅，能放开我吗？",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-26"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "莉薇娅",
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@谁要放开你啊",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-27"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@就是因为即便展开被膜，小彩羽还是希望与你共存@你才能进来吧？",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-28"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@让宇宙存活这件事本身，我还是表扬你一下吧",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-29"
      },
      {
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@所以，我不能为了宇宙而活@而是必须为了你而活",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-30"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "丘比",
        "narration": "―丘比―@…………",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-31"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "十七夜",
        "narration": "―十七夜―@看来是暂时放弃了",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-32"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "御魂",
        "narration": "―御魂―@那么，老师，让我们在别处再会吧",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-33"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "莉薇娅",
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@下次见面的时候，事情到底会变成什么样呢",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-34"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "御魂",
        "narration": "―御魂―@我可能已经当上了市长哦？",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-35"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "十七夜",
        "narration": "―十七夜―@我也可能已经是警察局长了",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-36"
      },
      {
        "nameNarration": "莉薇娅",
        "narration": "―莉薇娅―@哈哈，那就太好了@我这还是第一次期待未来",
        "voiceFullAuto": "fullvoice/section_103306/vo_full_103306-6-37"
      },
